    {
      "chinese": "「pasuntamul」的慶祝儀式，即是將酒糟拋向天神、地靈和萬物之靈的謝恩之祭。其意涵是再次與天地萬物之靈建立更誠摯的情誼關係，盼望著年年蒙受天地萬物之降福，人類的農作再次充滿大地，穀物雜糧之收穫推高至天之渴望。也表示將在新的一年裡，族人仍然能夠大吉大利。",
      "ab": "Maca sinluc’an is pasuntamul dii ha, makucias tamuli’ masisaupas daza’ a Diqanin, nastu’ a qavic ciin alminanan a is’angi’ tuqumic masumsum. \r\n[===]\r\nMaca sinpasnava’ dii ha, ala sintupa tu katnuang muqna pakacial is alminanan a is’ang ha’an aidalaqan ti’, mala’acqut ca sinpakadaidaz, min’asaz tu katnuang malqamisan tuqumicunang is cikaupa ka miniqumic ha’an dalaq ti’, maca sincucuaz a muqna’ang mindia’ mincicia ha’an dalaq ti’, min’asaz amin tu katnuang macinqauzu’ ca sinlalading ha’an pantilacan cina qaitu’. Ala sintupa tu katnuang ca bunun ha’an tatqamisan dii muqnang kabahi’ ca iniqumican.",
      "order": "4",
